            "title": "紐油曾見96.5美元  布油收跌2.7%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國際油價下跌，美伊戰爭或結束，此外美國石油庫存增幅高於預期。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"油價\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20200413-CH-oil_FB-1-1-1-1-3-1-1-1-2-3-1-1_source-ap_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"油價\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20200413-CH-oil_FB-1-1-1-1-3-1-1-1-2-3-1-1_source-ap_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">油價</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">紐約期油5月合約一度回落4.81%，低見每桶96.5美元，收報100.12美元，跌1.2% ; 倫敦布蘭特期油6月合約收報每桶101.16美元，跌2.7%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美國總統特朗普表示美國快將結束對伊朗的戰爭，消息影響油價。此外，美國能源信息署(EIA)數據顯示，美國上星期原油庫存大幅增加550萬桶，增幅遠高於預期，庫存增至近3年高位。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15826441-%e7%b4%90%e6%b2%b9%e6%9b%be%e8%a6%8b96-5%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83-%e5%b8%83%e6%b2%b9%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c2-7",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/8a6d6fb35c89d9b0db4c4846f290c2c3_Iran_US_Oil_Prices_19824_FB.jpg.webp",
